{"tid":1942070,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"英超8強聯名上書，要求曼城在禁令上訴期間不得參加歐冠比賽","createTime":"2020-03-24T23:22:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T23:28:42.000Z","uid":173952,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d49f415ecf16f3f8422f78f19cfd371f7731f3e0","tid":1942070,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T23:22:43.000Z","msg":"3月25日訊據《每日郵報》的消息，英超前10球隊中​​，有8支（除了曼城和謝菲聯外）向最高仲裁庭聯名上書，要求曼城在禁令上訴期間不得參加歐冠比賽。<br />\n<br />\n 此前，由於違反財政公平條約，曼城被歐足聯處以2年不得參加歐戰的禁令，不過曼城方面已向最高仲裁庭提起了上訴。"},{"pid":"cf59e320b07f9c30eef51aee79c1f41f1ee3a438","tid":1942070,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T23:23:08.000Z","msg":"英超聯合軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c697d8fed7b524094cb7d306676cbe6e7f388694","tid":1942070,"uid":84081,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T23:26:51.000Z","msg":"都合理<br />\n<br />\n轉會禁令既上訴期間都唔畀買人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31fe1522dce467d525a890cd9cc3374a98b41669","tid":1942070,"uid":261118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T23:28:14.000Z","msg":"擺明搞你，點會比你上訴得直，事實你又真係走漏違規，咁遲早都要禁，今季又打得咁差，早d禁左重整旗鼓仲好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac560d0fdd3bec9629028aa9a75f602ec5db0371","tid":1942070,"uid":261118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31fe1522dce467d525a890cd9cc3374a98b41669","tid":1942070,"uid":261118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T23:28:14.000Z","msg":"擺明搞你，點會比你上訴得直，事實你又真係走漏違規，咁遲早都要禁，今季又打得咁差，早d禁左重整旗鼓仲好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T23:28:42.000Z","msg":"走漏洞"}]}